headlines.title: MTV VJ & Talk Show Host Was 52
headlines.description: Former MTV VJ and talk show host Ananda Lewis has died.

headlines.title: College students, agitators and a Hamptons brat among 86 arrested at rowdy NYC anti-ICE protest
headlines.description: Police said 86 anti-ICE protesters were charged on Tuesday, while city officials vowed not to let the Big Apple get out of control like LA.

headlines.title: RFK Jr. names members of CDC vaccine committee after firings
headlines.description: The new members will join the Advisory Committee on Immunization Practices, or ACIP, which advises the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention.

headlines.title: About 500 National Guard troops in LA are trained to accompany agents on immigration raids
headlines.description: About 500 of the National Guard troops deployed to the Los Angeles protests have been trained to accompany agents on immigration operations, the commander in charge said Wednesday.

headlines.title: Harris Yulin, character actor and Broadway star, dies at 88
headlines.description: Actor had over 100 credits including Scarface, Training Day, Rush Hour 2, Frasier, Ozark and Clear and Present Danger

headlines.title: US military can temporarily detain protesters in Los Angeles, commander says
headlines.description: The commander overseeing military operations in Los Angeles said that troops deployed to the city can temporarily detain individuals but cannot make arrests.

headlines.title: Google prepares to 'reduce' Pixel 6a battery in coming updates
headlines.description: Code in Android 16 suggests that Google will "reduce" battery life on the Pixel 6a due to an overheating risk

headlines.title: Star Of Broadway, TV & Film Was 87
headlines.description: Harris Yulin, the acclaimed actor who starred in such Broadway productions as Hedda Gabler and The Price, and in films such as Scarface, has died.

headlines.title: L.A. immigration raid protests: Full coverage of curfew, arrests, troops
headlines.description: At least 14 people are facing federal charges tied to L.A. immigration protests as more demonstrations pop up around the U.S. Also, a Republican senator is threatening to investigate local immigrant advocates.
